{"tid":627010,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"CITY仔有感而發","createTime":"2018-04-12T15:11:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-19T05:21:49.000Z","uid":137555,"like":9,"dislike":68,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"fbc72be3398bb833ee87d16d9f0c759e02b560c7","tid":627010,"uid":137555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T15:11:27.000Z","msg":"作為一個CITY仔<br />\n我對呢間野都冇咩好感<br />\n因為呢間野冇科係真係講得上係TOP<br />\n無論社科 文科 商科 甚至法律 <br />\n冇一科係可以stand out<br />\n新開既獸醫又未成氣候<br />\n今年ENGINE收分又奇低 <br />\n而且係campus入邊既活動範黎黎去去都係個幾棟主要大樓入面<br />\n甚少接觸到陽光 <br />\n<br />\n但係如果BEST 5有21-23分<br />\nCITY商科絕對係你一個物超所值既選擇<br />\n如果入左C.Finance/會計/marketing/Finance<br />\nDepartment同商學院會不斷SEND internship/workshop/exchange報名資料比你<br />\n基本上你肯報就一定去到/有OFFER CV唔使愁冇野寫<br />\n去外國EXCHANGE一般會有20K左右既資助 <br />\n而且商學院一直以黎都係CITY既發展重點<br />\n商科學生較受重視 唔同理工浸大<br />\n一個重理 一個重文<br />\n加上CITY呢幾年不斷有外資注水<br />\n成間U仲有發展 刷排名既潛力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講左咁多 都係希望幫吾城商科宣傳下<br />\n希望大家唔好屌得咁應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n吾城商科絕對係比上不足 比下有餘既選擇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\nCity 商科 vs poly商科<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/417887/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/417887/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n城大獸醫第一屆DSE收分（新鮮出爐）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/437979/page/7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/437979/page/7</a><br />\n<br />\n馬會捐城大5億建健康一體化大樓<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hkcd.com/content/2017-11/22/content_1071902.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcd.com%2Fcontent%2F2017-11%2F22%2Fcontent_1071902.html&d=tcVB8DBkPI5NzQNp5hlX6xv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=644072cd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkcd.com/content/2017-11/22/content_1071902.html</a><br />\n<br />\n中銀香港慶百周年 億元捐贈城大<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.boc.cn/big5/aboutboc/ab8/201707/t20170728_9878227.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.boc.cn%2Fbig5%2Faboutboc%2Fab8%2F201707%2Ft20170728_9878227.html&d=tcVB8DBkPI5NzQNp5hlX6xv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=e3572a1d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.boc.cn/big5/aboutboc/ab8/201707/t20170728_9878227.html</a>"},{"pid":"59ece43279ab464a849c48d0ced01b646fdfb3b1","tid":627010,"uid":2389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T15:13:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"de36ef89d9db92269369a5b86bb4fbb57b3798ac","tid":627010,"uid":59518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T15:16:49.000Z","msg":"點睇ms department<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de4d6d6af8a751679223775e8ef7d6b0cc17e23e","tid":627010,"uid":137555,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"de36ef89d9db92269369a5b86bb4fbb57b3798ac","tid":627010,"uid":59518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T15:16:49.000Z","msg":"點睇ms department<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T15:17:43.000Z","msg":"一個好多錢既DEPARTMENT"},{"pid":"ba9d365e568e00976fc9b8b1111522fbf0afb5ce","tid":627010,"uid":132968,"like":54,"dislike":8,"score":46,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T15:22:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/12/232226_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F12%2F232226_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif&h=d2e032e1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"70d496d41883fe55d8b3795cb048d0248a430cae","tid":627010,"uid":4070,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T15:23:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a88ad4b62366f49fda42aa14bcf38d5c66a97966","tid":627010,"uid":132968,"like":10,"dislike":3,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201